blockquote>洛瓦索以中國駐法大使館為例，使館一再釋放不實新聞。其中包括法國療養院員工拋下工作崗位，集體遺棄老人，讓他們餓死、病死，還說「歐洲面對疫情的態度不負責任」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"多啲翻譯畀外國知,支共最興用殘體出fake news抹黑外國"},{"pid":"c514d5eb50745f49ecc1550708d56a06fcfc3aea","tid":2214671,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aea75b4519e3fd8e054c35179065d724589c9070","tid":2214671,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"44f1c9a6028322107f48ca4b7714dacc8bda2acc","tid":2214671,"uid":45213,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洛瓦索以中國駐法大使館為例，使館一再釋放不實新聞。其中包括法國療養院員工拋下工作崗位，集體遺棄老人，讓他們餓死、病死，還說「歐洲面對疫情的態度不負責任」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"多啲翻譯畀外國知,支共最興用殘體出fake news抹黑外國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">北京大外宣踢鐵板 法國外長召見中國大使表達不滿</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/04/15 14:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200415/4760x3171_941933365499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200415%2F4760x3171_941933365499.jpg&h=a7697200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國外長勒德里安（圖）14日召見中國駐法大使盧沙野，表達對中國近日相關言行的不滿。（中新社提供）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者曾婷瑄巴黎14日專電）<span class=\"red\">中國駐法大使館企圖在法國推動大外宣，誇耀中國抗疫模式並批評西方國家處理不當。法國外長勒德里安今日召見中華人民共和國駐法大使盧沙野，以表達對中國近日相關言行的不滿。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200415/6960x4667_80151502181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200415%2F6960x4667_80151502181.jpg&h=f5f6dec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國外長勒德里安14日召見中國駐法大使盧沙野（圖），表達對中國近日相關言行的不滿。（中新社提供）<br />\n<br />\n勒德里安（Jean-Yves Le Drian）在新聞稿中首先提及自2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情12月開始後，「中法兩國保持互助，包括兩國間相互運送防疫物資」。然而，「中國駐法大使近日公開場合的立場，並不符合兩國良好的雙邊關係」。<br />\n<br />\n勒德里安表示，「我在召見時，清楚傳達我對中國駐法大使近日言行的不贊同」。根據法媒表示，所指言行與中國大使館透過宣傳手段，誇耀中國政府抗疫「勝利」，同時批評西方國家危機治理有關。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國大使館12日於官網張貼一篇名為「把顛倒的事實再顛倒過來 &mdash;&mdash;一名中國駐法國使館外交官對新冠肺炎疫情的觀察」的文章。文中批評西方國家抹黑中國，並毫無根據的指控法國「養老院護理人員擅離職守，集體逃離，導致老人成批餓死、病死」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AntoineBondaz/status/1249599448554057728?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoineBondaz%2Fstatus%2F1249599448554057728%3Fs%3D20&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9mmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d7975305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoineBondaz%2Fstatus%2F1249599448554057728%3Fs%3D20&h=67fe03ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AntoineBondaz/status/1249599448554057728?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n此文引發許多議論，策略研究基金會（FRS）研究員與巴黎政治學院（Sciences Po）<span class=\"red\">教授波恩達茲（Antoine Bondaz）便表示，「中國大使館的這篇文章，又再一次丟盡顏面。謠言、不實資訊、侮辱全都有。不反應、不譴責，就是放任一個大使可以胡作非為，連一點尊重都沒有」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於外長召見盧沙野一事，無國界記者組織法國總部主席Pierre Haski（韓石）表示贊同。他在推特上表示：「這是期待中的，也是必須的。外長勒德里安因中國張貼令人無法容忍的文章後召見大使。大使館的推特現在變得可親多了。」（編輯：陳政一）1090415<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pierrehaski/status/1250135140422029319?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpierrehaski%2Fstatus%2F1250135140422029319%3Fs%3D20&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9mmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=b8a44f81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpierrehaski%2Fstatus%2F1250135140422029319%3Fs%3D20&h=bc7556c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pierrehaski/status/1250135140422029319?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004150018.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202004150018.aspx&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9mmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=6c333817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004150018.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"ff238e9802d98c37b26a12659683f69790e24e3c","tid":2214671,"uid":18120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"習交好嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續加速啦，地球靠你哋喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74bad63c6f0da146210a71a9764732ec7c2d43b","tid":2214671,"uid":106929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16cb73a31e0dd5c99033f6757126d0db89aa9736","tid":2214671,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"比人撚返轉頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"支那人一慣套路 大話講一百次 不斷講 就過關"},{"pid":"329d10a31da7f07d64681ccb93e043e121cd756f","tid":2214671,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"中國抱怨受害不實新聞 歐盟議員：別做賊喊抓賊"},{"pid":"d5b129a2a0e85507ea13c39d7829e7961121ba10","tid":2214671,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"希望大家真係認清<br />\n唔好好似64咁 得個講字"},{"pid":"10977b5e08f7bb122b855a901463903e799d1b92","tid":2214671,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵撚死"},{"pid":"977e01da9204708cc6d7f9defa48651e0dd41d48","tid":2214671,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒出國際"},{"pid":"ec1763597d78768f4ff36057c3381e7564fb1ceb","tid":2214671,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco